snippet.textDisplay: Bhai hum to ghar se khaane ka samaan leke gye the. Paani plane pe hi manga tha. Kisi ne mask k liye nhi bola. Puri flight chabar chabar khaate travel kiya. To garib bihari ko ullu bnana asan hai jo kabhi ✈️ pe nhi gye.. paani v free me milta hai. Or vistara me khana bhi free milta hai.. to ye sab jhhhut hai.. aise hi bihari badnam nhi hai..
